desc.en:
The London Underground is the urban rail transit system of London, England, it is the world's first subway, which was completed and opened to traffic on January 10, 1863. Underground cars run underground in central London and above ground to the suburbs, with 55% of the cars running on surface.
London has built a total of 408 kilometres of underground network, of which 160 kilometres are underground, with 12 lines and 275 stations in operation
desc.zh-Hans:
伦敦地铁是英国伦敦的城市轨道交通系统，它是世界上第一条地铁，于1863年1月10日建成通车。地铁车辆在伦敦市中心地底运行，至郊区在地面运行，其中地面运行线路占55%。
伦敦已经建成总长408公里的地铁网，其中160公里在地底，共有12条线路、275个运作中的车站
